{"data":[{"id":559739517,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bfe7f9abcbc9202a2b8adda00f11019f","url_token":"chen-jing-76-80","name":"陈京","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/06e1e0820fc6e6e7cc23a61d1aeb512f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/06e1e0820fc6e6e7cc23a61d1aeb512f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bfe7f9abcbc9202a2b8adda00f11019f","user_type":"people","headline":"资深工程造价人员。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2045,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559739517","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545757415,"updated_time":1545758783,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":107,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"need_payment","content":"\u003cp\u003e大晚上的，我正在加班做商务标，实在是搞不下去了抽空看看知乎，怎么就看到这么搞笑的一道问题儿……容我先笑几分钟……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本人不才，数学方面最高荣誉是中学阶段的奥赛广东省二等奖，以及高考数学基本满分，所以我觉得我有资格回答此问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的回答是：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，则不需要保送。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e这个问题有点类似于：(在单注情况下)我兜里有3600万元，正好能把双色球所有的组合统统买下来，那么我是不是就能中500万呢……\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e答案是：肯定可以啦！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不过你既然有3600万元，为啥要中这区区500万？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e你都能证明哥猜，你还会看得上区区清北？？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e所以，题主就是个数学基本没入门、不知天高地厚的生瓜蛋子一个……大家随便笑笑就散了吧……\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我继续做标书去了……哈哈哈哈……真搞笑这个问题。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp